Kernel driver it87
==================

Out-of-tree hwmon driver for ITE Super I/O chips.
Based on upstream Linux kernel drivers/hwmon/it87.c with additional chip support.

Maintained by IT-Kuny <https://github.com/IT-Kuny/UGREEN-Fan-Control>

Supported chips:
  * IT8603E/IT8623E
    Prefix: 'it8603'
    Addresses scanned: from Super I/O config space (8 I/O ports)
    Datasheet: Not publicly available
  * IT8613E  ← UGREEN DXP2800 (primary target)
    Prefix: 'it8613'
    Addresses scanned: from Super I/O config space (8 I/O ports)
    Datasheet: Not publicly available
  * IT8620E
    Prefix: 'it8620'
    Addresses scanned: from Super I/O config space (8 I/O ports)
