    Guenter Roeck <linux@roeck-us.net>


Kernel Compatibility
--------------------

Requires kernel 6.1 or later. No compat.h shims needed.
Tested on:
  * Debian 13 (trixie), kernel 6.12.74


Building & Installing
---------------------

Production build (default, debug symbols stripped):

  make clean
  make
  sudo make install

Development build (debug symbols included):

  make BUILD=dev
  sudo make install

Using DKMS (recommended for persistence across kernel updates):

  sudo make dkms

To remove DKMS installation:

  sudo make dkms_clean

Loading the module:

  sudo modprobe hwmon-vid
  sudo modprobe it87 ignore_resource_conflict=1


Module Parameters
-----------------

* update_vbat: int
  0 if vbat should report power on value, 1 if vbat should be updated after
  each read. Default is 0.

* fix_pwm_polarity: int
  Force PWM polarity to active high (DANGEROUS). Some chips are
  misconfigured by BIOS. Only use if fan speed control is inverted.

* force_id: ushort
  Force chip ID to specified value. Should only be used for testing.

* ignore_resource_conflict: bool
  Ignore ACPI resource conflicts (similar to acpi_enforce_resources=lax,
  but only affects this driver). Required on most systems. Default: 0.
  Note: May cause race conditions in rare cases. Use with awareness.


Hardware Interfaces
-------------------

All chips are LPC Super-I/O chips accessed through the LPC bus (ISA-like
I/O ports).


Fan Speed Control
-----------------

Manual PWM mode is supported on all chips. Automatic "Smart Guardian" mode
is implemented for older chips (IT8705F up to rev F, IT8712F up to rev G).

To configure fan control, use pwmconfig after loading the driver:

  sudo sensors-detect
  sudo pwmconfig
  sudo systemctl enable --now fancontrol


Reporting Unsupported Chips
---------------------------

Run sensors-detect and note the chip ID, then:

  sudo isadump -k 0x87,0x01,0x55,0x55 0x2e 0x2f 7
  sudo isadump 0x295 0x296

Open an issue at https://github.com/IT-Kuny/UGREEN-Fan-Control/issues
with the output and your board type.
